parameters.name: InsertWay
parameters.description:
The method to submit URLs to be prefetched.

Valid values:

*   **textBox**
*   **oss**

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the scheduled prefetch task.

parameters.name: OssUrl
parameters.description: The URL of the OSS object that stores the URLs to be prefetched.

parameters.name: SiteId
parameters.description: The website ID, which can be obtained by calling the [ListSites](~~2850189~~) operation.

parameters.name: UrlList
parameters.description: The URLs to be prefetched. This parameter is required if you set InsertWay to textBox.
